reviewText: Australia was so-so. I thought it would never end and I stopped caring about the characters (except the young man) after about 30 minutes. Marigold Hotel is cute, but not very memorable. I really liked My Life in Ruins and watched it twice. I really liked Descendants and watched it twice!
I just loved this movie... So many talented people made this movie one I will watch many more times. A great story line with each characters life unique .
